{"tid":752784,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【全裸冰火體驗】田中圭意外露股 焗完桑拿再浸冰風呂","createTime":"2018-07-23T05:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T08:23:06.000Z","uid":27064,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a392c14fa29864aebc0a851a7885f0a997fee43f","tid":752784,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180723/large/1532318472_a965.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180723%2Flarge%2F1532318472_a965.jpg&h=b1d5c5f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本BL神劇《大叔的愛》大受歡迎，播出後掀起連串現像及製造話題，更帶挈男主角田中圭人氣急升，入行18年，終於令佢有一套代表作。<br />\n<br />\n田中圭喺《大叔的愛》中飾演戇直男主角春田創一，在職場捲入複雜嘅HEHE關係，角色令觀眾對田中圭好感度大增，目前佢正夥拍吉岡里帆、遠藤憲一嘅富士台新劇《健康而有文化的最低限度生活》，近日就剝衫上綜藝節目谷劇。<br />\n田中圭近日亮相晨早節目全裸入鏡，雖然電視台有經過後期加工遮住重要部位，不過有網民就發現部份鏡頭，從鏡中倒影睇到田中圭不慎露股。田中今次應要求進行浴場及桑拿體驗，佢一絲不掛上陣，唔止走入乾蒸房搞到㷫合合，仲落埋冰風呂，搞到佢七情上面兼O晒嘴，場面搞笑。原來田中圭半紅不黑逾十年，一直鍾情傳統風呂，以前一星期會去足五日，不過近年已甚少到浴場，現時爆紅更加冇時間去公共浴場浸浴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180723/large/1532318474_efd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180723%2Flarge%2F1532318474_efd7.jpg&h=f777dae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180723/large/1532318474_9992.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180723%2Flarge%2F1532318474_9992.jpg&h=0631e083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180723/large/1532318475_b25d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180723%2Flarge%2F1532318475_b25d.jpg&h=0da591c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180723/large/1532318478_8643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180723%2Flarge%2F1532318478_8643.jpg&h=91eb3afc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180723/large/1532318484_af96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180723%2Flarge%2F1532318484_af96.jpg&h=5e8dbb2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180723/58475132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F58475132&d=7PxwOGkTbeXZjwJBTQNWwQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=fdf7c958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F58475132&h=e05dfd50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180723/58475132</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edaaeb93eaff183ee0d8377e3f7316d8c6ee76a1","tid":752784,"uid":3189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:55:27.000Z","msg":"好白<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfb389d380afb685818cc9f8988f80bb5692eae","tid":752784,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b330cef716080fd076975036b6ad735c91c08fe3","tid":752784,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":